Bodies in Alliance //Politics of the Street by Marinella Senatore: In 2012 five members of the Russian protest punk group Pussy Riot demonstrated against Russian President Vladimir Putin’s re-election. In 2018 they dressed like police officers and invaded the Fifa World Cup finals in Moscow.
